          "id": "medmcqa-dc7722be-17b0-476e-8895-bcc8bc7b43bb",
          "text": "Traumatic dislocation of epiphysial plate of femur occurs -a) Mediallyb) Laterallyc) Posteriorlyd) Rotationallye) Anteriorly",
