          "explanation": "The usual protocol is : -\n\n\nFirst give neoadjuvant chemotherapy (Pre-operative chemotherapy).\nNeo-adjuvant chemotherapy is followed by surgery : - This may be limb salvage surgery (most of the time) or amputation depending on the situation.\nSurgery is followed by postoperative chemotherapy."
