          "explanation": "Boutonniere deformity: flexion contracture of PIP joint and extension of DIP jointSwan neck deformity: Hyperextension of PIP joint and flexion at DIP jointZ-deformity: radial detion of the wrist with ulnar detion of fingers(Refer: Mohindra's Fundamentals of Ohopedics, 2nd edition, pg no. 420)",
