          "id": "medmcqa-c877f72f-f464-4751-8f73-527a37c8edf2",
          "text": "A 15-year-old boy is injured while playing cricket. X-rays of the leg rule out of a possible fracture. The radiologist repos the boy has an evidence of aggressive bone tumor with both bone destruction and soft tissue mass. The bone biopsy reveals a bone cancer with neural differentiation. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis?",
