          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "In Colles fracture, Stiffness of the fingers (commonest) and malunion are common complications. Other complications seen occasionally are - Sudeck&;s osteodystrophy, carpal tunnel syndrome, and rupture of the extensor pollicis longus tendon. ref : Maheswari 9th edition Pg: 114",
