          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Ans. B. To differentiate between structural and postural scoliosis* Adams forward bend test helps to differentiate functional and structural scoliosis.* Functional scoliosis will disappear on forward bending while structural scoliosis will not.",
          "hint": "Topic: Peripheral Nerve Injuries"
