          "explanation": "Myositis ossificans, Conservative treatment is the method in acute stages. * Immobilisation of the pa by splints *Drugs-diphosphonate, calcitonin, NSAIDS *late stages- physiotherapy to regain movement *surgical excision REF:- Ebnezar- 3rd edn- pg no 41",
