          "explanation": "\"Ameloblastoma is the most common jaw tumour\" -- Radiology of head & Neck\n\"Ameloblastoma is the most common tumour of the maxillomandibular region. The mandible is affected in 75% of cases, the maxilla in 25%\". -- Oral pathology"
