          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Hangman fracture - through pedicle and lamina of C2 veebra / Spondylolisthesis of C2 over C3Jefferson's fracture - through body of C1 veebraClay Shoveler fracture - Avulsion spinous process of T1 > C7 veebra(Refer: Mohindra's Fundamentals of Ohopedics, 2nd edition, pg no. 222)",
